<h1 class='property-title'>perspective-origin</h1>
<p class='property-description'>The <code>perspective-origin</code> <a title="CSS" rel="internal" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS">CSS</a> property determines the position the viewer is looking at. It is used as the <em>vanishing point</em> by the <code><a rel="custom" href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/CSS/perspective">perspective</a></code>
 property.</p>